            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>廣汽埃安（AION）宣佈登陸香港市場，首家陳列室日前開幕。品牌同日發布了旗下全新純電動車 AION Y Plus ，慶祝埃安九龍灣陳列室開幕。廣汽埃安同場亦展示了 AION ES。現在就讓小編帶大家先睹為快，看看廣汽埃安這 2 部右軚車吧。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217740" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240128155807-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240128155807-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240128155807-1-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>全新開業的埃安九龍灣陳列室位於九龍東商業大廈「第一集團中心」，毗鄰大型商場和郵輪碼頭，其設計以簡約、時尚風格為主。陳列室內還設有新能源充電展示區，幫助客户瞭解充電配套設備及如何充電操作。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217744" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240128160654-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240128160654-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240128160654-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217743" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240128180533-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240128180533-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240128180533-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲新能源充電展示區</p><h2>AION Y Plus</h2><p>廣汽埃安表示，旗下 AION Y Plus 將會於今年 5 月正式進入香港市場。AION Y Plus 定位是「科技頭等艙」，NEDC 標準續航里程為 490KM。是次在陳列室展出的是右軚版本。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217741" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240128160623-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240128160623-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240128160623-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217742" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240128160635-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240128160635-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240128160635-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217753" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/420769369_3827754243-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/420769369_3827754243-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/420769369_3827754243.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>廣汽埃安亦照顧到消費者對車內儲物空間的需求，AION Y Plus 後備箱空間十足，能夠輕鬆放入 3 個大行李箱。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217751" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/420726932_2437775233-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/420726932_2437775233-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/420726932_2437775233.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217754" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/421104684_9085122975-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/421104684_9085122975-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/421104684_9085122975.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>如果對露營有興趣的朋友也可以考慮這輛車，AION 方面表示這輛車可以搬走整個露營營地，符合露營愛好者需求。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217752" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/420845676_9073389444-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/420845676_9073389444-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/420845676_9073389444.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>規格</p><table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; height: 294px;"><tbody><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;" colspan="2">基本規格</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">長 × 寬 × 高（mm）</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px; text-align: center;">4535 × 1870 × 1650</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">軸距（mm）</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px; text-align: center;">2750 mm</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">座位</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px; text-align: center;">5</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">最大功率（kW）</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px; text-align: center;">150 kW</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">最大扭距（Nm）</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px; text-align: center;">225Nm</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">電池類型</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px; text-align: center;">磷酸鐵鋰電池</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">電池能量（kWh）</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px; text-align: center;">61.5 kWh</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">續航里程（km）（NEDC 標準）</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px; text-align: center;">NEDC：490 km</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">轉向系統</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px; text-align: center;">電動助力轉向系統（EPS）</td></tr><tr style="height: 54px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 54px;">懸掛系統</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 54px; text-align: center;"><table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;"><tbody><tr><td style="width: 100%;">前：麥花臣式獨立懸掛系統</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 100%;">後：扭力桿懸掛系統</td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table><table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; height: 144px;"><tbody><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 100%; height: 24px;" colspan="2">外飾</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">17 吋，鋁合金輪圈</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">外後視鏡電動調節</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">LED 大燈</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">外後視鏡電動摺疊</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">LED 日間行車燈</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">外後視鏡發熱功能</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">後霧燈</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">電動隱藏式門把手</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">外後視鏡集成轉向燈</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;"></td></tr></tbody></table><table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; height: 288px;"><tbody><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;" colspan="2">內飾</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">I PEDAL 電子踏板</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">多功能軚盤</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">無鑰匙進入</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">優質仿真皮座椅</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">10.25 吋液晶儀表</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">司機席電動座椅</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">14.63 吋觸控中控螢幕</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">四門車窗一觸式升降功能（帶防夾功能）</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">車載音響系統（支援英文、繁體中文及不同語言）</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">全景天窗（帶電動遮陽簾）</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">手機藍牙連接</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">司機座椅靠背可完全放平</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">6 揚聲器 Bongiovi 大師品牌音效</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">第二排座椅 40/60 摺疊全放平</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">自動空調</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">32 種顏色車廂氛圍燈</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">PM 2.5 濾網</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">前排 12V 電源</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">後排空調出風口</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">前／後排 USB 接口</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">優質仿真皮軚盤</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">內後視鏡頭帶 USB 接口（5V）</td></tr></tbody></table><table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; height: 240px;"><tbody><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 100%; height: 24px;" colspan="2">安全</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">後備輪胎</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">前排安全帶未扣燈光提示及聲響</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">防鎖死制動系統（ABS）</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">ISOFIX 兒童座椅接口號</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">電子車身穩定系統（ESP）</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">自動駐車 Auto Hold</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">電子制動力分配（EBD）</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">牽引力控制系統（TCS）</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">制動能量回收系統</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">胎壓監測系統</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">前排雙安全氣囊</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">定速巡航</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">前排側氣囊</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">倒車雷達（後雷達）</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">側氣簾</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">360° 高清全景泊車</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">前排限力式安全帶</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;"></td></tr></tbody></table><h2></h2><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/26/xiaomi-su7-ev-28-dec-launch/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">官方微博開啟車章曝光，小米 SU7 電動車 28/12 發表</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/23/toyota-recalled-bz3-ev-in-china/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">剩餘電量顯示比實際高，一汽豐田召回 2.5 萬部安全隱患 bZ3 電動車</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/10/31/benz-smart1/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">仁孚引入兩款全新 smart #1 電動車，預計 2024 年首季可正式交付</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>AION ES</h2><p>廣汽埃安亦展出了另一款右軚版本 AION ES。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217756" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/420502410_7850599467-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/420502410_7850599467-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/420502410_7850599467.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>AION ES 是廣汽埃安針對出行市場的特供車，使用 136 馬力電動機，電池容量為 50.6kWh，一次充電續航里程可達 442 公里（NEDC）。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217757" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/421023911_1304094856-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/421023911_1304094856-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/421023911_1304094856.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>同場加映：Hyper SSR</h2><p>陳列室開業當天，除了新的右軚版本 AION Y Plus 及 AION Es 外，廣汽埃安亦於同場展出 Hyper SSR。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217748" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240128160748-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240128160748-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240128160748-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Hyper SSR</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217759" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240128160834-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240128160834-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240128160834-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Hyper SSR</p><p>Hyper SSR 是埃安旗下高級豪華車系 Hyper （昊鉑）的首款車型，擁有前 1 後 2 三電機，電驅峯值總功率達 900kW，採用前後雙叉臂懸架，實現極致操控性和乘坐舒適性。</p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/26/xiaomi-su7-ev-28-dec-launch/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">官方微博開啟車章曝光，小米 SU7 電動車 28/12 發表</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/23/toyota-recalled-bz3-ev-in-china/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">剩餘電量顯示比實際高，一汽豐田召回 2.5 萬部安全隱患 bZ3 電動車</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/10/31/benz-smart1/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">仁孚引入兩款全新 smart #1 電動車，預計 2024 年首季可正式交付</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/29/gac-aion/life-tech/auto/">廣汽 AION 強勢襲港　Y Plus、ES 右軚版雙傑打響頭炮</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
